title: Holiday Gift Bag
description:
Our ISMÊ Signature Gift Bag is the perfect finishing touch for holiday gifting, designed to elevate your present while keeping things simple and authentic.

The gift bag is made from sturdy white paper with our gold ISMÊ logo and soft rope handles. It includes our signature gold tie ribbon to finish the look once assembled.

Please note:
To ensure safe shipping, this gift bag will arrive unfolded inside a non-branded protective bubble polymailer, along with the gold tie ribbon. The bag will not arrive pre-assembled or tied. Customers will need to place the bikinis inside the bag and assemble it themselves.

This is the exact packaging we use, just shipped flat to protect it in transit.

Perfect for Christmas gifting, birthdays, or anyone who loves a thoughtful, elevated presentation.

title: PITAYA - Boyshorts
description:
The Pitaya Boyshorts bring a playful, vintage-poolside vibe with the perfect ISMÊ twist. Designed in our vibrant pink ribbed fabric and framed with the signature black-and-white stripe tie waistband, these shorts offer comfort, coverage, and curve-hugging softness in one.

Fully adjustable ties with hand-beaded ends let you style them high-rise for a snatched look or low-rise for a relaxed, 90s feel. Whether you’re by the pool or styling them street-side, they’re your new essential pink moment.

— Soft ribbed texture

— Adjustable tie waistband with beads

— Wear high or low rise

— Matches the Pitaya Triangle Top

title: PITAYA - High Cut Bottoms
description:
Our Pitaya High Cut Bottoms are designed to sculpt, elongate, and flatter from every angle. Made in our vibrant ribbed pink and outlined with the signature black-and-white stripe trim, this bottom brings a bold, playful contrast to your swim look.

The cinched back seam creates a natural butt-lift effect, enhancing your curves while still feeling effortless and comfortable. Fully versatile, the sides can be worn high on the hips for a leg-lengthening cut or low rise for a relaxed, not super cheeky fit.

— Ribbed pink fabric with striped outline

— High cut silhouette

— Cinched back seam for a flattering lift

— Wear high or low rise

— Designed to match the Pitaya Triangle Top

title: PITAYA - Adjustable Bottoms
description:
Meet the Pitaya Adjustable Bottoms: pink statement trimmed with our signature black-and-white striped outline. Designed with ultra-thin, fully adjustable side ties that sculpt to your body, this bottom gives you your dream fit every single time.

Each side is finished with oversized amber resin beads — the signature Pitaya touch — adding a luxe, playful pop that catches the sun beautifully. Minimal coverage, silky-soft stretch, and that unmistakable ISMÊ silhouette.

Your new favorite tanning bottom… and the final drop of 2025.

title: PITAYA - Bandeau Top
description:
The Pitaya Bandeau Top is your effortlessly chic, ultra-versatile pink moment. Made in our vibrant ribbed fabric and outlined with bold black-and-white stripes, this style features a removable striped necktie finished with hand-beaded ends for that signature ISMÊ detail.

Designed with discreet side structure bars and an inner silicone grippy lining, this bandeau stays comfortably in place while maintaining its shape

Wear it strapless, tied as a halter, styled as a bow, or completely clean — the look is entirely up to you. The fully adjustable back allows a personalized fit, while the removable bowtie adds a playful touch whenever you want it.

— Ribbed pink fabric with striped middle band

— Removable striped halter tie with beaded ends

— Fully adjustable back

— Optional bowtie detail

— Versatile, supportive, and perfect for tan lines

— Matches all Pitaya bottoms

description:
Embrace Hawaiian vibes with Jasmin — a triangle bikini top in baby yellow ribbed fabric. Adorned with three delicate charms:

This design captures the essence of island vibration. Turquoise bead charms at the strap ends complete the look, reminiscent of Hawaii’s serene waters and vibrant coastal hues. Perfect for sunny escapes!
